  "texts": [
    "Striking the right balance between personalization and generalization is crucial to ensure practical and trustworthy healthcare guidance.",
    "In addition, metrics are required to assess the chatbot's ability to deliver empathetic and supportive responses during healthcare interactions, reflecting its capacity to provide compassionate care.",
    "Moreover, existing evaluations overlook performance aspects of models, such as computational efficiency and model size, which are crucial for practical implementation.",
    "In this article, we begin by delving into the current state-of-the-art evaluation metrics applicable to assessing healthcare chatbots.",
    "Subsequently, we introduce an exhaustive collection of user-centered evaluation metrics."
